urity and data models and structures. His position at the local level gave him the opportunity to bring different government administrations under one umbrella with a shared infrastructure (human and ICT resources). His involvement as an active member of the Linked Organisation for Local Authorities (LOLA) increased the network capacity in sharing knowledge and best practices in Europe but also worldwide. As a protagonist of bringing ICT up to a management level and vice versa, he creates a good understanding between the politicians, top management and ICT.'),(1349,350,'bio','President of LOLA'),(1350,350,'description',''),(1351,350,'time',''),(1352,350,'speaker',''),(1353,350,'_edit_last','1'),(1354,350,'_edit_lock','1389169405:1'),(1355,137,'speaker',''),(1356,351,'biography','Hanna Niemi-Hugaerts (MA in New Media) has an extensive experience on concept design for digital services. She currently works as a project manager at Forum Virium Helsinki on promoting and piloting open, interoperable APIs, pursuing new means to fuel developer engagement.'),(1357,351,'bio','Project Manager, Forum Virium Helsinki  '),(1358,351,'description',''),(1359,351,'time',''),(1360,351,'speaker',''),(1361,351,'_edit_last','2'),(1362,351,'_edit_lock','1387533923:2'),(1366,354,'_wp_attached_file','2013/12/richard-kerby.jpg'),(1367,354,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:80;s:6:\"height\";i:80;s:4:\"file\";s:25:\"2013/12/richard-kerby.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:1:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:23:\"richard-kerby-50x50.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:50;s:6:\"height\";i:50;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:10:{s:8:\"aperture\";i:0;s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";i:0;s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";i:0;s:3:\"iso\";i:0;s:13:\"shutter_speed\";i:0;s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";}}'),(1368,354,'_wp_attachment_image_alt','Mr. Richard Kerby'),(1369,326,'_thumbnail_id','354'),(1371,355,'_w