y: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Scoop EUR 5,000, EUR 10,000 or even EUR 20,000?</span></span></span>\r\n<p lang=\"\"></p>\r\n<p lang=\"en-GB\">\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">To promote the</span></span></span><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> exciting innovation possibilities made available through </span></span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Open Data, </span></span></span><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">DataDays</span></span></span><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> are launching three new </span></span></span><strong><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Hackathon</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> competitions! </span></span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">The competitions are sponsored and supported by, CORVE, V-ICT-OR, iDROPS and OKFN Belgium.</span></span></span><span><!-- Maybe be better to show the sponsors for each individual competition? --></span>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span>Open Belgium Competition’s</span></span></span></strong>\r\n<p lang=\"en-GB\"><span style=\"color: #66696d;\">Are you a programmer or designer? A hacker through and through? </span></p>\r\n<span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">If so you can </span></span></span><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><i>be the first </i></span></span></span><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">to start working on what may well be Flanders most valuable data set - the VKBO, ‘the Enhanced Crossroads Bank for Enterprises’ - in which all enterprises, schools, hospitals etc. are geographically localised. Using the VKBO and Uit datasets in Vlaanderen, you can develop an application, produce mashups or create visualisations and present them to the public.</span></span></span>\r\n<p lang=\"en-GB\">\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">1. Professional Hackathon</span></span></span></span></strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Would you like to start your own company or launch a commercial application? If so, take part in the ‘Professional </span></span></span><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Hackathon:’ </span></span></span>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Produce a working application </span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Draft a business plan to present the results to citizens and entrepreneurs </span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Preferably use data from the VKBO and other datasets applied throughout Flanders as a whole. </span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Develop a plan detailing how you can further market the app, which may result in your nomination for Apps4EU.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">The Government of Flanders’ expects that applications should be up and running with a maximum of </span></span></span><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">EUR 20.000.</span></span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Criteria for </span></span></span><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">entry include: 1) quality of the application, 2) price for making the application permanently available for at least three years and 3) sustainability of the app. The application may be further marketed by the developer.</span></span></span>\r\n<p lang=\"en-GB\">\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">2. H</span></span></span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">ack for Good: Lets Fight Poverty!</span></span></span></span></strong><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">\r\nOver 30 ideas offering solutions to specific poverty related issues were conceived during eight creative miniLABs across Flanders. </span></span></span><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Hack For Good</span></span></span><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> wants to turn these ideas into reality. We are asking digital developers, business developers, coders, programmers and hackers to pitch a plan to a panel of financiers on how to implement the ideas that they think are best. </span></span></span><strong><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">The best project will win</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> EUR 10,000 </span></span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: #66696d;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">to boost social innovation. </span></span></span></strong>\r\n<p lang=\"en-GB\"><span style=\"color: #66696d;\">Criteria for entry include: xxxxx</span></p>\r\n<p lang=\"\">\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span>Open Europe</span></span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Droid Sans\', \'Times New Roman\';\"><span> | Open World Competition</span></span></span></stro