C Online), iDEAL (Holland) of bank transfer.\r\n\r\n<b>Invoices</b>\r\n\r\nYou will receive a confirmation e-mail stating the details of your purchase and the total amount paid upon registration. The ticketing system does not provide invoices automatically, though.\r\n\r\nIf you would need an invoice, you can <a title=\"invoice\" href=\"mailto:jessica.vandendries@bz.vlaanderen.be\" target=\"_blank\">send us</a> the ticket details, so we can prepare an invoice for you. Don’t forget to mention you VAT number!\r\n\r\n<b>Refund policy</b>\r\n\r\nAllData Days tickets are non-refundable, however we make it very easy to transfer your ticket to another person.\r\n\r\nTo transfer your ticket, simply contact our <a title=\"Ticket transfer\" href=\"mailto:sarah.buelens@bz.vlaanderen.be\" target=\"_blank\">help desk</a> with your transfer request and our awesome support team will help you.','Registration','','inherit','closed','open','','213-revision-v1','','','2013-11-29 12:35:13','2013-11-29 12:35:13','',213,'http://www.datadays.eu/213-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(257,2,'2013-12-17 08:53:21','2013-12-17 08:53:21','','Dr. Ali Al Khouri: Open Data and Government Decision Support Systems','','inherit','closed','open','','225-autosave-v1','','','2013-12-17 08:53:21','2013-12-17 08:53:21','',225,'http://www.datadays.eu/225-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(258,2,'2013-12-03 11:36:53','2013-12-03 11:36:53','','Prof. Dr. Ali Al-Khouri ','','publish','closed','closed','','258','','','2013-12-20 10:41:01','2013-12-20 10:41:01','',0,'http://www.datadays.eu/?post_type=dd-speaker&#038;p=258',8,'dd-speaker','',0),(259,2,'2013-12-03 11:43:19','2013-12-03 11:43:19','','Mr. Gérald Santucci','','publish','closed','closed','','gerald-santucci-2','','','2013-12-20 10:41:56','2013-12-20 10:41:56','',0,'http://www.datadays.eu/?post_type=dd-speaker&#038;p=259',7,'dd-speaker','',0),(260,1,'2013-12-04 08:52:57','2013-12-04 08:52:57','','hero','','inherit','closed','open','','hero','','','2013-1