.datadays.eu/?post_type=dd-speaker&#038;p=502',0,'dd-speaker','',0),(503,3,'2014-01-27 08:59:01','2014-01-27 08:59:01','','Lorenzo Pillizzari','','inherit','closed','open','','lorenzophoto','','','2014-01-27 08:59:01','2014-01-27 08:59:01','',502,'http://www.datadays.eu/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Lorenzophoto.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(504,3,'2014-01-27 09:26:31','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Tom Van Herck','','draft','closed','closed','','','','','2014-01-27 09:26:31','2014-01-27 09:26:31','',0,'http://www.datadays.eu/?post_type=dd-speaker&#038;p=504',0,'dd-speaker','',0),(505,2,'2014-01-27 09:32:54','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','closed','open','','','','','2014-01-27 09:32:54','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://www.datadays.eu/?p=505',0,'post','',0),(506,2,'2014-01-27 09:34:50','2014-01-27 09:34:50','<b>Data Days – Tickets &amp; registration</b>\r\n\r\nData Days is a three-day conference in Ghent, Belgium, exploring how open data is changing the way the Public Sector innovates and delivers services:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Open Belgium\" href=\"http://www.datadays.eu/open-belgium/\" target=\"_blank\">Open Belgium (17 Feb)</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Open Europe\" href=\"http://www.datadays.eu/open-europe/\" target=\"_blank\">Open Europe (18 Feb)</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Open World\" href=\"http://www.datadays.eu/open-world/\" target=\"_blank\">Open World (19 Feb)</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>Data Days registration</b>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nData Days is a three-day conference, allowing you to follow certain modules or chose a full conference ticket.\r\n\r\nFor registration <strong>please use a recent version of your browser. The system may have reduced or no function with IE8 or older versions. If you have any problems registering, please use another browser. You can contact us about your registration issues <a title=\"Registration Data Days\" href=\"mailto:sarah.buelens@bz.vlaanderen.be\" target=\"_blank\">by mail</a>.</strong>\r\n\r\nAfter registration you will receive a confirmation e-mail stating the details of your purchase and the total amount paid upon registration, if not, do not hesitate to contact us.\r\n\r\nAll pricing is in Euros and includes VAT and handling fees. No additional charges will be made.\r\n\r\n1 Day ticket:  100 Euro\r\n\r\n2 Days ticket:  160 Euro\r\n\r\n3 Days ticket: 200 Euro\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<b>Press &amp; media accreditation</b>\r\n\r\nAs a journalist or media professional, you can apply for a media accreditation <a title=\"Media accreditation\" href=\"mailto:sarah.buelens@bz.vlaanderen.be\" target=\"_blank\">here </a>, allowing for full access to the conference and the possibility to put in interview requests.\r\n\r\n<b>Payment methods</b>\r\n\r\nOnline ticket payments are handled <b>100% securely</b> and through all the common payment methods: Visa, Mastercard, Paypal, Bancontact, American Express, Homebanking (Dexia netbanking, ING Homepay and KBC Online), iDEAL (Holland) or <strong>bank transfer</strong>.\r\n\r\n<b>Invoices</b>\r\n\r\nYou will receive a confirmation e-mail stating the details of your purchase and the total amount paid upon registration. The ticketing system does not provide invoices automatically, though.\r\n\r\nIf you would need an invoice, you can <a title=\"invoice\" href=\"mailto:jessica.vandendries@bz.vlaanderen.be\" target=\"_blank\">send us</a> the ticket details, so we can prepare an invoice for you. Don’t forget to mention you VAT number!\r\n\r\n<b>Refund policy</b>\r\n\r\nAllData Days tickets are non-refundable, however we make it very easy to transfer your ticket to another person.\r\n\r\nTo transfer your ticket, simply contact our <a title=\"Ticket transfer\" href=\"mailto:sarah.buelens@bz.vlaanderen.be\" target=\"_blank\">help desk</a> with your transfer request and our awesome support team will help you.','Registration','','inherit','closed','open','','213-revision-v1','','','2014-01-27 09:34:50','2014-01-27 09:34:50','',213,'http://www.datadays.eu/213-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(507,2,'2014-01-27 09:37:07','2014-01-27 09:37:07','<b>Data Days – Tickets &amp; registration</b>\r\n\r\nData Days is a three-day conference in Ghent, Belgium, exploring how open data is changing the way the Public Sector innovates and delivers services:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Open Belgium\" href=\"http://www.datadays.eu/open-belgium/\" target=\"_blank\">Open Belgium (17 Feb)</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Open Europe\" href=\"http://www.datadays.eu/open-europe/\" target=\"_blank\">Open Europe (18 Feb)</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"Open World\" href=\"http://www.datadays.eu/open-world/\" target=\"_blank\">Open World (19 Feb)</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>Data Days registration</b>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nData Days is a three-day conference, allowing you to follow certain modules or chose a full conference ticket.\r\n\r\nFor registration <strong>please use a recent version of your browser. The system may have reduced or no function with IE8 or older versions. If you have any problems registering, please use another browser. You can contact us about your registration issues <a title=\"Registration Data Days\" href=\"mailto:sarah.buelens@bz.vlaanderen.be\" target=\"_blank\">by mail</a>.</strong>\r\n\r\nAfter registration you will receive a confirmation e-mail stating the details of your purchase and the total amount paid upon registration, if not, do not hesitate to contact us.\r\n\r\nAll pricing is in Euros and includes VAT and handling fees. No additional charges will be made.\r\n\r\n1 Day ticket:  100 Euro\r\n\r\n2 Days ticket:  160 Euro\r\n\r\n3 Days ticket: 200 Euro\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<b>Press &amp; media accreditation</b>\r\n\r\nAs a journalist or media professional, you can apply for a media accreditation <a title=\"Media accreditation\" href=\"mailto:sarah.buelens@bz.vlaanderen.be\" target=\"_blank\">here </a>, allowing for full access to the conference and the possibility to put in interview requests.\r\n\r\n<b>Payment methods: online or bank transfer\r\n</b>\r\n\r\nOnline ticket payments are handled <b>100% securely</b> and through all the common payment methods: Visa, Mastercard, Paypal, Bancontact, American Express, Homebanking (Dexia netbanking, ING Homepay and KBC Online), iDEAL (Holland). You can also select <strong>bank transfer</strong>.\r\n\r\n<b>Invoices</b>\r\n\r\nYou will receive a confirmation e-mail stating the details of your purchase and the total amount paid upon registration. The ticketing system does not provide invoices automatically, though.\r\n\r\nIf you would need an invoice, you can <a title=\"invoice\" href=\"mailto:jessica.vandendries@bz.vlaanderen.be\" target=\"_blank\">send us</a> the ticket details, so we can prepare an invoice for you. Don’t forget to mention you VAT number!\r\n\r\n<b>Refund policy</b>\r\n\r\nAllData Days tickets are non-refundable, however we make it very easy to transfer your ticket to another person.\r\n\r\nTo transfer your ticket, simply contact our <a title=\"Ticket transfer\" href=\"mailto:sarah.buelens@bz.vlaanderen.be\" target=\"_blank\">help desk</a> with your transfer request and our awesome support team will help you.','Registration','','inherit','closed','open','','213-revision-v1','','','2014-01-27 09:37:07','2014-01-27 09:37:07','',213,'http://www.datadays.eu/213-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(508,2,'2014-01-27 09:57:01','2014-01-27 09:57:01','','DataDays Hackaton awards','','inherit','closed','open','','221-autosave-v1','','','2014-01-27 09:57:01','2014-01-27 09:57:01','',221,'http://www.datadays.eu/221-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(509,3,'2014-01-27 11:16:12','2014-01-27 11:16:12','','Mr. Tom Van Herck','','publish','closed','closed','','mr-tom-van-herck','','','2014-01-27 11:16:12','2014-01-27 11:16:12','',0,'http://www.datadays.eu/?post_type=dd-speaker&#038;p=509',0,'dd-speaker','',0),(510,3,'2014-01-27 11:14:59','2014-01-27 11:14:59','','Tom Van Herck','','inherit','closed','open','','_mg_5981','','','2014-01-27 11: